msgid ""
"The Quarkus HTTP server listens on the HTTPS port (default `8443`) for both TCP (HTTP/1.1, HTTP/2) and UDP (HTTP/3 over QUIC) traffic.\n"
"There is no separate port for HTTP/3."
msgstr "El servidor HTTP de Quarkus escucha en el puerto HTTPS (por defecto, `8443` ) tanto el tráfico TCP (HTTP/1.1, HTTP/2) como el UDP (HTTP/3 sobre QUIC). No existe un puerto específico para HTTP/3."

